description:
In this karaoke version of Jesus, Hold My Hand, I'll be sharing all the lyrics  so you can sing along with me.
This song is a popular gospel classic and is always a crowd favourite. Whether you're a churchgoer or not, this karaoke version of Jesus, Hold My Hand is a great way to spend some quality time with friends and family. So grab a friend and get ready to belt out the lyrics!

Songwriter: Andrew Johnson
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters karaoke youtube
